<div class="home-v2-new" id="homev2"><div class="hv2-bg" id="hv2bg"></div><div class="hv2-decor"><span class="orb"></span><span class="ring"></span><span class="leaf"></span><span class="mist"></span><span class="mist"></span><span class="mist"></span></div><nav class="hv2-dock" aria-label="Home V2 quick navigation"><a href="#hero" class="active">Home</a><a href="#programs">Programs</a><a href="#results">Results</a><a href="#plans">Plans</a><a href="#stories">Stories</a><a href="#contact">Start</a></nav><main class="hv2-main"><section class="hv2-section hv2-hero" id="hero"><div class="hv2-container"><span class="kicker">Coach Osama Omran — O2F.life</span><h1>Transform your body, from the inside out.</h1><p>Personalized coaching that combines training, nutrition, anti-aging direction, and performance follow-up in one clear transformation journey.</p><a class="hv2-btn" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Start your transformation</a></div></section><section class="hv2-section compact" id="intro"><div class="split"><article class="panel glass"><span class="kicker">The full system</span><h2>A science-driven, nature-backed approach.</h2><p>O2F brings coaching, nutrition direction, performance habits, anti-aging guidance, and transformation follow-up into one premium journey. Every visitor should understand the system in seconds: choose a path, see how progress is tracked, compare plans, and start.</p><div class="tag-row"><span class="pill">Training</span><span class="pill">Nutrition</span><span class="pill">Anti-aging</span><span class="pill">Follow-up</span></div><div class="media-strip"><div class="media-tile" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517836357463-d25dfeac3438?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80')"></div><div class="media-tile" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498837167922-ddd27525d352?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80')"></div><div class="media-tile" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506126613408-eca07ce68773?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80')"></div></div></article><div class="photo glass"><img src="/assets/images/hero.jpeg" alt="Coach Osama Omran"><div class="stats"><span>20+<br><small>Years</small></span><span>1000+<br><small>Clients</small></span><span>100%<br><small>Custom</small></span><span>24/7<br><small>Support</small></span></div></div></div></section><section class="hv2-section" id="programs"><div class="hv2-container"><div class="section-head"><span class="kicker">Choose your path</span><h2>Three focused routes inside one transformation system.</h2><p>Anti-aging, Methylene Blue education, and training transformation are grouped as premium glass tabs so the page stays short, clean, and visually rich.</p></div><div class="tabs-shell glass"><div class="tabs-nav" role="tablist"><button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="anti" type="button">Anti-Aging</button><button class="tab-btn" data-tab="blue" type="button">Methylene Blue</button><button class="tab-btn" data-tab="training" type="button">Training Transformation</button></div><article class="tab-panel active" id="tab-anti" data-theme="anti"><div class="tab-copy glass"><span class="kicker">Longevity direction</span><h3>Age with better energy, recovery, and daily performance.</h3><p>A clean route for vitality, recovery habits, smarter lifestyle routines, and long-term wellness follow-up.</p><div class="benefit-grid"><div class="benefit"><b>Recovery</b><span>Sleep, stress load, and routine control.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Vitality</b><span>Nutrition and habits that support daily energy.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Consistency</b><span>Simple follow-up that keeps the plan realistic.</span></div></div><div class="mini-journey"><span>Assess lifestyle</span><span>Build routine</span><span>Track progress</span></div></div><div class="tab-visual glass"><span class="visual-icon">A+</span><div class="visual-caption"><b>Longevity rhythm</b><p>Recovery, nutrition, movement, and routine design in one calm track.</p></div></div></article><article class="tab-panel" id="tab-blue" data-theme="blue"><div class="tab-copy glass"><span class="kicker">Cellular energy</span><h3>Methylene Blue presented as a clear performance education route.</h3><p>A premium simple section around focus, energy, cellular performance, and proper professional guidance.</p><div class="benefit-grid"><div class="benefit"><b>Focus</b><span>Positioned around mental clarity and alertness.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Energy</b><span>Explains the cellular performance concept visually.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Guidance</b><span>Directs visitors to safe professional consultation.</span></div></div><p class="note">Guidance-first approach. Ask before starting.</p></div><div class="tab-visual glass"><span class="visual-icon">MB</span><div class="visual-caption"><b>Blue performance</b><p>Educational, clean, and consultation-first — no confusing claims.</p></div></div></article><article class="tab-panel" id="tab-training" data-theme="fit"><div class="tab-copy glass"><span class="kicker">Body transformation</span><h3>Training, nutrition, and follow-up built around your body and lifestyle.</h3><p>A structured route for fat loss, muscle gain, athletic shape, and long-term body transformation.</p><div class="benefit-grid"><div class="benefit"><b>Training</b><span>Goal-based workout planning.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Nutrition</b><span>Food direction that fits daily life.</span></div><div class="benefit"><b>Follow-up</b><span>Adjustments based on real progress.</span></div></div><div class="mini-journey"><span>Assess</span><span>Plan</span><span>Transform</span></div></div><div class="tab-visual glass"><span class="visual-icon">FIT</span><div class="visual-caption"><b>Transformation route</b><p>Workout, food, and adjustments working together weekly.</p></div></div></article