icker">Start now</span><h2>Ready to start your transformation?</h2><p>Choose your path and let O2F guide your next version with a clear plan, visual progress, and direct support.</p><a class="hv2-btn" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Contact and subscribe</a></article><div class="faq"><article class="bubble glass"><b>Is this only training?</b><p>No. It combines training, nutrition, and ongoing follow-up.</p></article><article class="bubble glass"><b>Not sure where to start?</b><p>Send your goal and current level, then the right route can be selected.</p></article><article class="bubble glass"><b>What makes it different?</b><p>It is built around your goals, schedule, lifestyle, and current level.</p></article></div></div></section></main></div><script>(function(){var root=document.getElementById('homev2');var bg=document.getElementById('hv2bg');var tabs=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn'));var panels=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.tab-panel'));var dock=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.hv2-dock a'));var sections=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.hv2-section[id]'));function fx(){var max=root.offsetHeight-window.innerHeight||1;var p=Math.max(0,Math.min(1,-root.getBoundingClientRect().top/max));root.style.setProperty('--scroll',Math.round(p*1000));bg.style.setProperty('--bg-x',(Math.sin(p*4)*24)+'px');bg.style.setProperty('--bg-y',(-p*260)+'px');bg.style.setProperty('--bg-scale',(1.14+p*.08).toFixed(3));root.style.setProperty('--light-y',(-p*120)+'px');var current=sections[0];sections.forEach(function(s){var r=s.getBoundingClientRect();if(r.top<window.innerHeight*.45&&r.bottom>window.innerHeight*.2){current=s;}});dock.forEach(function(a){a.classList.toggle('active',a.getAttribute('href')==='#'+current.id);});}tabs.forEach(function(btn){btn.addEventListener('click',function(){var target='tab-'+btn.getAttribute('data-tab');tabs.forEach(function(b){b.classList.toggle('active',b===btn);});panels.forEach(function(p){p.classList.toggle('active',p.id===target);});});});dock.forEach(function(a){a.addEventListener('click',function(e){var el=document.querySelector(a.getAttribute('href'));if(el){e.preventDefault();el.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',block:'start'});}});});window.addEventListener('scroll',fx,{passive:true});window.addEventListener('resize',fx);fx();})();</script>
